column2: select g.specObjID, g.ra, g.dec, s.z, s.plateID, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.run2d from galaxy g JOIN galSpecExtra e ON e.specObjID = g.specObjID JOIN specObj s ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID JOIN zooSpec z ON z.specObjID = g.specObjID JOIN zooVotes v ON v.specObjID = g.specObjID where e.bptclass = # AND s.z < .# AND (z.p_mg BETWEEN .# AND .#) AND v.nvote_tot > = # order by z.p_mg
